# 🎵 Music Player

This is a simple and beautiful **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript-based music player**.  
It allows users to **play, pause, skip, and enjoy music with a stylish interface**.

---

## 📁 Features

- 🎶 Play, pause, and resume songs  
- ⏭ Skip to next track (if added)  
- 🎨 Stylish layout with image and animation  
- 📱 Responsive on mobile and desktop  

---

## 📂 Project Structure

| File           | Description                     |
|----------------|---------------------------------|
| `music.html`   | Main HTML structure             |
| `music.css`    | Styling with custom design      |
| `music.js`     | JavaScript for music control    |
| `song.mp3`     | Demo song used for the player   |
| `music-img.jpeg` | Cover image used in layout    |

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository  
2. Open `music.html` in any browser  
3. Enjoy the music 🎧

